list.text: 'Hi {PT}, how are you feeling this week?'
' Thats okay. For how long have you felt this way?'
' Are you feeling tired or stressed? Or are you just waiting this feeling out?'
' Has anything changed in your medication since the last time you met {DR}'
' That's fine. And your diet? You are still eating well, yes?'
' Any relationship issues with friends or family recently? '
' Or did anything happen at work?'
' Have you spoken to anyone about it?'
' Would you like me to notify {DR} and arrange a phone call?'
